%E5%BA%93%E7%9A%84%E9%9A%94%E7%A6%BB%E7%BA%A7%E5%88%AB"><span class="nav-number">1.1.12.</span> <span class="nav-text">介绍一下数据库的隔离级别</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%8B%EF%BC%8C%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93%E7%B4%A2%E5%BC%95%E5%BA%95%E5%B1%82%E6%98%AF%E6%80%8E%E6%A0%B7%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%E4%B8%8B%E7%B4%A2%E5%BC%95%E4%BC%9A%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%88"><span class="nav-number">1.1.13.</span> <span class="nav-text">说明一下，数据库索引底层是怎样实现的，哪些情况下索引会失效</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#mysql%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%A4%E7%A7%8D%E5%BC%95%E6%93%8E-%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%AB"><span class="nav-number">1.1.14.</span> <span class="nav-text">mysql数据库的两种引擎 区别</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E8%AF%B7%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%8B%EF%BC%8C%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93%E7%B4%A2%E5%BC%95%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E6%97%B6%E5%80%99%E7%94%A8Innodb%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E6%97%B6%E5%80%99%E7%94%A8MyISAM%E3%80%82"><span class="nav-number">1.1.15.</span> <span class="nav-text">请介绍一下，数据库索引，以及，什么时候用Innodb什么时候用MyISAM。</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%E5%88%87%E5%88%86%E4%B8%8E%E5%9E%82%E7%9B%B4%E5%88%87%E5%88%86"><span class="nav-number">1.1.16.</span> <span class="nav-text">数据库水平切分与垂直切分</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#JDBC%E4%B8%AD%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%8B%E5%8A%A1%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%EF%BC%9F"><span class="nav-number">1.1.17.</span> <span class="nav-text">JDBC中如何进行事务处理？</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E6%98%AF%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93%E4%B8%AD%E4%BA%8B%E5%8A%A1%E7%9A%84ACID%EF%BC%9F"><span class="nav-number">1.1.18.</span> <span class="nav-text">什么是数据库中事务的ACID？</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8JDBC%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E7%BB%8F%E5%B8%B8%E9%81%87%E5%88%B0%E6%80%A7%E8%83%BD%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%EF%BC%8C%E8%AF%B7%E4%BD%A0%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%8B%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87%E8%AF%BB%E5%8F%96%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%9A%84%E6%80%A7%E8%83%BD%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%9A%84%E6%80%A7%E8%83%BD%EF%BC%9F"><span class="nav-number">1.1.19.</span> <span class="nav-text">使用JDBC操作数据库时，经常遇到性能问题，请你说明一下如何提升读取数据的性能，以及更新数据的性能？</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E8%AF%B7%E4%BD%A0%E8%AE%B2%E8%AE%B2-Statement-%E5%92%8C-PreparedStatement-%E7%9A%84%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%AB%EF%BC%9F%E5%93%AA%E4%B8%AA%E6%80%A7%E8%83%BD%E6%9B%B4%E5%A5%BD%EF%BC%9F"><span class="nav-number">1.1.20.</span> <span class="nav-text">请你讲讲 Statement 和 PreparedStatement 的区别？哪个性能更好？</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E8%AF%B7%E4%BD%A0%E8%A7%A3%E9%87%8A%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%8BJdo%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E5%AE%83%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8"><span class="nav-number">1.1.21.</span> <span class="nav-text">请你解释一下Jdo以及它的作用</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E8%B0%88%E8%B0%88JDBC%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%84%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E5%AE%83%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%9F"><span class="nav-number">1.1.22.</span> <span class="nav-text">谈谈JDBC的反射，以及它的作用？</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li></ol></div>
